Reasoning: The paper discusses the risks associated with spreadsheet usage and proposes a solution to reduce those risks. This falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) as it involves developing tools and techniques to improve the quality and reliability of software. Additionally, the paper mentions the importance of user experience and ease of use, which could fall under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also discusses the security of intellectual property contained in spreadsheets, which could fall under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR). Finally, the paper mentions the creation and deployment of web-based applications, which could fall under the category of programming languages (cs.PL) or cyber-physical systems (cs.CY).
